Drop font files here to activate the full design system:

  Extenda100-Regular.woff2   — hero & display text (Extenda 100)
  OpenSauceOne-Regular.woff2 — body copy, regular (400)
  OpenSauceOne-Medium.woff2  — body copy, medium (500)
  OpenSauceOne-Bold.woff2    — body copy, bold (700)

Without these files the site falls back to Bebas Neue (display) and DM Sans (body),
both loaded from Google Fonts. Shrikhand is always served from Google Fonts.
